      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Your exhaustion is real, but please do not let this thought of ending your life become your solution, as it is a momentary escape that can take your loved ones with you. If you feel like giving up, please reach out to a crisis line or emergency services immediately, because there are people who want to listen and help you through this darkness. You are not alone, and there is hope for relief and healing even when it feels impossible right now.",
      "source": "target",
